{
  "name": "Boil Release Acidic Dragons Breath",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Futton.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You fire a beam of acid in a straight line spreading a massive wave of corroding acid. Creatures in a 30-foot long, 5-feet wide line in front of you must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking 8d8 Acid damage, and gaining 2 ranks of Corroded on a failed save, or half as much on a successful one. Also, creatures, excluding you, within 5 feet of the beam must succeed a constitution saving throw taking 6d6 Acid damage and 1 rank of corroded on a failed save.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and damage by 2d8 and 2d6.</p>",
